file_content.text: Last dataspike in...got it! The droid factory's under House Thul control again.
Uh oh. Looks like House Ulgo's making one last try for it. Troops incoming!
I've rigged you up some help. Those droids have targeted Ulgo. Good luck.
Droid production's been shut down. One more dataspike and the factory's ours.
All right, I'm hacked in. Let's see if I can get that door open for you...got it!
